This Vagrant setup can be used to test Percona XtraDB Cluster (Percona Server with Galera)

This is used with Centos 6 x86_64.


How to use ?

vagrant up percona1
vagrant up percona2
vagrant up percona3

And this is all, you have now 3 servers running Percona XtraDB Cluster !

Note: init script provided in the package doesn't work :(

To start your server, you have to perform these steps on the 3 nodes:

mysql_install_db 
/usr/bin/mysqld_safe &
